---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — MyCGPA"
  description="Learn how MyCGPA protects your privacy. We don't collect or store your grades, GPA, or personal data. All calculations are done in your browser."
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="mesh-gradient" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="legal-hero container-page">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="display-xl page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="body-md subtitle">
          Last updated: June 9, 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legal Content -->
    <section class="legal-content container-page">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="toc-sidebar">
          <nav aria-label="Table of contents">
            <h2 class="toc-title">Contents</h2>
            <ul class="toc-list">
              <li><a href="#information-we-collect">Information We Collect</a></li>
              <li><a href="#how-we-use">How We Use Information</a></li>
              <li><a href="#data-storage">Data Storage</a></li>
              <li><a href="#cookies">Cookies & Tracking</a></li>
              <li><a href="#advertising">Advertising (Google AdSense)</a></li>
              <li><a href="#third-party">Third-Party Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="#your-rights">Your Rights</a></li>
              <li><a href="#children">Children's Privacy</a></li>
              <li><a href="#changes">Changes to Policy</a></li>
              <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="content-main card-level-2">
          <div class="legal-intro">
            <p class="body-lg">
              At MyCGPA, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our website and services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <section id="information-we-collect" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              <strong>We do NOT collect or store your academic data.</strong> All CGPA, GPA, and grade calculations are performed entirely in your browser using JavaScript. Your grades, courses, and results never leave your device.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              We may collect limited, non-personal information including:
            </p>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li>Browser type and version</li>
              <li>Device type and operating system</li>
              <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
              <li>Referring website or search terms</li>
              <li>General geographic location (country/region level)</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section id="how-we-use" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">2. How We Use Information</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              The limited information we collect is used to:
            </p>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
              <li>Analyze usage patterns and identify popular features</li>
              <li>Fix technical issues and optimize page load times</li>
              <li>Understand which universities and grading systems are most used</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="body-md">
              We do NOT use your data for advertising, profiling, or any commercial purposes beyond improving our free service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="data-storage" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              <strong>Local Storage Only:</strong> Any data you enter (grades, course names, credits) is stored only in your browser's local storage. This data remains on your device and is never transmitted to our servers.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              You can clear this local data at any time by clearing your browser's cache and cookies or using the "Clear Data" button in our calculator.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="cookies" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We use minimal cookies and tracking technologies:
            </p>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function (theme preference, calculator state)</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> To understand site usage (if you consent)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="body-md">
              Analytics and advertising cookies are only set after you consent via the cookie banner shown on your first visit. You can review or change your choice at any time via the "Cookie Settings" link in our footer. For a full breakdown of every cookie we use, see our <a href="/cookies/" class="email-link">Cookie Policy</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="advertising" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">5. Advertising (Google AdSense)</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We use Google AdSense to display advertisements on MyCGPA. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to this site and/or other sites on the Internet.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="email-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>, or opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="email-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aboutads.info</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="third-party" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We may use third-party services for:
            </p>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li><strong>Web Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics or similar tools (anonymized data only)</li>
              <li><strong>Content Delivery:</strong> CDN services to serve website files faster</li>
              <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Cloud infrastructure providers to host the website</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="body-md">
              These services have their own privacy policies. We ensure they do not access your grade calculations or academic data.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="your-rights" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">7. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              You have the right to:
            </p>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li>Access any personal data we may have collected</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
              <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
              <li>Request clarification about our data practices</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="body-md">
              Since we don't collect personal or academic data, most data rights are automatically protected by our privacy-first design.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="children" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              Our service is intended for students of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone. If you are a parent or guardian and believe we have inadvertently collected data about a child, please contact us immediately.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="changes" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The "Last updated" date at the top will reflect any changes. We encourage you to review this policy occasionally to stay informed.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              Significant changes will be announced on our homepage or via prominent notice on the website.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="contact" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">10. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <p class="body-md">
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@mycgpa.com" class="email-link">support@mycgpa.com</a>
              </p>
              <p class="body-md">
                <strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond within 48 hours.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="legal-cta container-page">
      <div class="cta-inner card-level-3">
        <h2 class="display-lg cta-title">Your privacy is protected</h2>
        <p class="body-md cta-desc">
          All calculations happen in your browser. Your grades stay private.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/#calculator" class="btn-primary">Try Calculator</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-5xl);
  }

  .legal-hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-mute);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Content Layout */
  .legal-content {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Table of Contents */
  .toc-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .toc-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm) 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .toc-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-xxs);
  }

  .toc-list a {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .toc-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-link);
  }

  /* Main Content */
  .content-main {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
  }

  .legal-intro {
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .legal-intro p {
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .legal-section strong {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .contact-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .email-link {
    color: var(--color-link);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .email-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .legal-cta {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .cta-desc {
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-on-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .content-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-sidebar {
      position: static;
      background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--spacing-xs);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .legal-hero {
      padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .content-main {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
